			</div>

			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-8">
					<h2>We are ...</h2>
					<p>First World Delivery was founded in 1979 with one location and only three employees. Today, we have over 300 team members in 5 regional service center locations across the country and an additional 90 agent offices. Our privately-owned business has grown into being one of the top logistics companies in the nation, arranging freight shipping services on a global scale. Due to our extensive nationwide presence and experience, we are positioned to provide a solution for any of your logistics needs, no matter how extensive, with the best customer service you’ll see in the industry.</p>
				</div>

