			          LOGISTICS SOLUTIONS
			        </a>
			      </h4>
			    </div>
			    <div id="collapseThree" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingThree">
			      <div class="panel-body">
			        Whether it’s through process evaluation, cost analysis, RFP administration, shipment optimization, or a totally custom approach, we’ll help you make sense of your supply chain. Let us be your trusted partner. We’re not just in the business of freight arrangement – we also offer a wide range of logistics and supply chain management services. Whether you only need a little extra help with your supply chain or you’re looking to outsource logistics management for the majority of your operations, we have a full menu of services for you to choose from.
			      </div>
			    </div>
